{"tid":1543853,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"良心作家天航：夢遊至台灣的香港人 如有需要 歡迎inbox他","createTime":"2019-09-05T10:47:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T16:39:07.000Z","uid":209097,"like":57,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"fd62abcea27ce3129e4502ba38b4ddade54ae68f","tid":1543853,"uid":209097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T10:47:35.000Z","msg":"熟悉我的讀友都應該知道，我是主修心理學系畢業的。<br />\n夢遊是很嚴重的精神疾病(mental disorder)。我所知最嚴重的案例，病患甚至會自行搭飛機到外國。<br />\n有聞不久前有香港人夢遊搭飛機到台灣，因為缺錢買回程機票而有家歸不得。如果大家認識\b當事人，歡迎叫他們聯絡我，就算我親自幫不了忙，也可以介紹台灣朋友去關照一下。至少我知道可以該去哪裡看醫生、中醫、牙醫和手上有些餐券。。總之助人為快樂之本，有需要歡迎inbox我！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/152506018099285/posts/3008336042516254?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F152506018099285%2Fposts%2F3008336042516254%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=g6cJT0UyhZ9RanxftZ%2B8MJKhd8YmQljH21R%2F5cbT5WU%3D&h=2db1b7be\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/152506018099285/posts/3008336042516254?sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"0282fc9e1c0024223ca18de578bce4c01d37a7ad","tid":1543853,"uid":209097,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T10:48:01.000Z","msg":"推到有夢遊嘅人見到"},{"pid":"c7094fba84129031b49d144ad0130ae58cfcb076","tid":1543853,"uid":233009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T10:48:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5c9c405dcf364caa137ea753271b3d6ef2d231c5","tid":1543853,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T10:49:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">撤LLM 對準政權</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3E7OjKb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3E7OjKb.gif&h=66b4ea40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uZFWW8o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuZFWW8o.jpg&h=4196affc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zNutjAi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzNutjAi.jpg&h=1817afe5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">得到黨媒認證</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sELTeyX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsELTeyX.png&h=0e8c0efe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">#Chinazi旗係一個符號，不斷向世界輸出反共思想！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">#Chinazi 赤納粹</span></span></strong><br />\nChinazi就係China+Nazi。<br />\n赤=共產紅色恐怖, 納粹不解釋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"> 全民反共 對準政權！</span></span></strong><br />\n黑警、黨鐵，港共全部都係人民既敵人<br />\n而背後一直有一個終極大Boss中共<br />\n<br />\n呢一刻中共絕對係十個煲得兩個蓋，準備爆煲。<br />\n今日唔號召世界圍堵中共，更待何時？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">用#Chinazi黎connect全世界</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">1. Connect所有黃絲。</span></strong><br />\n殘酷既現實係，並唔係所有黃絲都支持勇武。但黃絲最驚就係共產黨打到黎，一於用反共connect呢班淺黃!<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">2. Connect部分中立/藍絲。</span></strong><br />\n中立/藍絲既上一輩，全部都係親身經歷過六四既年代，唔少甚至係大陸生活過。係大陸生活上所面對既不公義、中共點砌人生豬肉、佢地可能比我地感受更深。佢地唔會否認對共產黨既恐懼！一齊黎喚醒佢地對中共既不信任！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">3. Connect全世界</span></strong><br />\nNazi既惡行到今時今日都依然係全世界既傷口，但佢地未必注意到係21世紀有個同Nazi不遑多讓既Chinazi！用#chinazi旗加海量文宣，話比佢地知我地既共同敵人係中共！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>目標：全香港市民都知到呢個符號！<br />\n請大家用各種創意方法令大家知道呢道Chinazi旗！<br />\n記住！存在即勝利！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">雙手奉上</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/02/9dojRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2F9dojRG.png&h=baf47345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXMrzU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXMrzU3.jpg&h=4fd76574&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f9e3b07d371bbc8f48b0e046856ee3d1555f7cc0","tid":1543853,"uid":209097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T10:50:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3793c948e1c2dea458a473271787e22406bc4a23","tid":1543853,"uid":258862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T10:51:24.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n雖然唔太鍾意睇佢嘅書，但respect"},{"pid":"6780e24f28101632acb640d56e19c39092a7b1bb","tid":1543853,"uid":268106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T10:51:36.000Z","msg":"良心作家呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65cfd1bd25d0e348d14ca15db4f6a0b141ae1dfd","tid":1543853,"uid":209097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T10:53:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"28ba58cec06ed47a5d5e7656b7870689a9436b3f","tid":1543853,"uid":203797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T10:53:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1743c09e2ef6f7ec7dd2ed542c7bfba2bc61d589","tid":1543853,"uid":60924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T10:54:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />多一條路就一條路"},{"pid":"fc73fd539784110ba7a0d127e7636bc00ee129d7","tid":1543853,"uid":209097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T10:55:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ae20475a6ba57be348f4b3b82fbe60f43af6603f","tid":1543853,"uid